==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Smothered mate
<hw>Smoth"ered mate</hw>. <fld>(Chess)</fld> <def>Checkmate given when
movement of the king is completely obstructed by his own men. This can
only occur when an opponent moves a knight into a position to give a
check to the king.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smotheriness</ent>⟦br⟧
